headline: Hewlett Packard Enterprise: Fiscal Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: SPRING, Texas (AP) — Hewlett Packard Enterprise Co. (HPE) on Thursday reported fiscal fourth-quarter net income of $175 million. The Spring, Texas-based company said it had profit of 11 cents per share. Earnings, adjusted for one-time gains and costs, were 62 cents per share.

content.title: Hewlett Packard Enterprise: Fiscal Q4 Earnings Snapshot
content.summary: SPRING, Texas (AP) — Hewlett Packard Enterprise Co. (HPE) on Thursday reported fiscal fourth-quarter net income of $175 million. The Spring, Texas-based company said it had profit of 11 cents per share. Earnings, adjusted for one-time gains and costs, were 62 cents per share.
